{
  "title": "Logs Explorer",
  "uid": "logs-explorer",
  "tags": ["cdc", "logs", "loki"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "10s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Log Volume by Level",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({level=~\".+\"}[$__interval])) by (level)",
          "legendFormat": "{{level}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "No logs in Loki. Ensure CDC consumer is configured to export logs via OTLP.",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "fillOpacity": 100,
            "lineWidth": 0,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" },
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" }
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "ERROR" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "error" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "WARN" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "yellow", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "warn" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "yellow", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "INFO" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "info" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "DEBUG" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "blue", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "debug" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "blue", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Application Logs",
      "type": "logs",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 6, "w": 24, "h": 12 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{application=~\".+\"} | json",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "noValue": "No logs available. Logs are currently output to container stdout. Configure OTel logging exporter for Loki integration."
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": true,
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Error Logs",
      "type": "logs",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 18, "w": 24, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{level=~\"ERROR|error\"} | json",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "noValue": "No error logs found."
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": true,
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Setup Instructions",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 26, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Logs Integration Status\n\nCurrently, the CDC consumer outputs logs to stdout in JSON format. To enable Loki integration:\n\n1. **Add OpenTelemetry Logback Appender** to `build.gradle.kts`:\n   ```kotlin\n   implementation(\"io.opentelemetry.instrumentation:opentelemetry-logback-appender-1.0\")\n   ```\n\n2. **Configure logback.xml** with the OTel appender\n\n3. **Restart the CDC consumer** to enable log export via OTLP\n\nFor now, use `docker logs cdc-consumer-k6 -f` to view logs."
      }
    }
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "level",
        "type": "custom",
        "options": [
          { "text": "All", "value": "", "selected": true },
          { "text": "Error", "value": "ERROR", "selected": false },
          { "text": "Warn", "value": "WARN", "selected": false },
          { "text": "Info", "value": "INFO", "selected": false },
          { "text": "Debug", "value": "DEBUG", "selected": false }
        ],
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "" },
        "query": "",
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "multi": false
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "version": 2
}
